gram\": \"July\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The religious gesture is prohibited under Article 3 of the IJF Code of Ethics.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The religious gesture\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"Article\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"the IJF Code\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"Ethics\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serb, who won the 2023 European Championship and the World Championship in 2017, and was the runner-up in the -90kg category at the World Championship this year, is now suspended from participating in all tournaments, camps, and preparations for the next five months.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"score\": 0.6538352949923281, \"rank\": 0.5078119633838437, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2023 European Championship\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championship\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"the runner-up\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the -90kg category\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championship\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"all tournaments\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"camps\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"the next five months\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the decision, Majdov said on Instagram that he was 'sorry that such a beautiful and difficult sport like judo has fallen to such things'.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.999999999999545