86, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was banned from participating in all tournaments, camps and preparations.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all tournaments\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"camps\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'True, in the defence letter of the disciplinary proceedings I did not want to apologise\\u2026 and of course I did not, nor will I ever, although I did not even know what the punishment could be.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the defence letter\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"the disciplinary proceedings\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"the punishment\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Lord has given me everything, both for me personally and for my career, and he is number 1 for me and I am proud of that.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Lord\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that will not change under any circumstances.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any circumstances\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Glory to Him and thanks for everything.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Glory\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"